		<div class="md-interesting-facts-box fact-box-details md-striped md-content-module-right">
        <div class="fact-box">
            <!DOCTYPE HTML><dl data-label="did you know?"><dt class="fact-list">did you know?</dt><dd><ul class="imars-list-itemized"><li>In 2005, Bill and Melinda Gates were designated Time Magazine's "Persons of the Year," along with the musician Bono.<br></li> <li>Queen Elizabeth II knighted Bill Gates in 2005.<br></li> <li>At age 31, Bill Gates became the youngest American billionaire, a record that held from 1987 until 2010, when Mark Zuckerberg became a billionaire at age 23.<br></li></ul></dd></dl></div>
